dinosaurs.name: Tyrannosaurus
dinosaurs.description: Tyrannosaurus Rex means Tyrant Lizard and were one of the biggest meat eaters.

dinosaurs.name: Majungasaurus
dinosaurs.description: May have indulged in cannibalism. Was 2 car lengths long. Weighed as much as a Rhinoceros. Ran on two legs. Was one of the last dinosaurs to have lived

dinosaurs.name: Sauroposeidon
dinosaurs.description: Fossils have been found in Oklahoma, Wyoming and Texas. Weighed as much as 10 elephants. As high as a 6 story building. Was 10 car lengths long. Its neck length was 40 feet long

dinosaurs.name: Edmontosaurus
dinosaurs.description: Edmontosaurus weighed as much as 2 Black Rhinoceros. Was over 4 car lengths long. Was about 2 stories high. Its name means “Edmonton Lizard”. Lacked a bony crest like other hadrosaurids

dinosaurs.name: Deinocheirus
dinosaurs.description: May have climbed trees like modern sloths. Deinocheirus is the largest bird mimic of all time. Weighs as much as an African Elephant. Was 3 car lengths long. Was as large as a Tyrannosaurus Rex. Had 10 inch claws and 8 foot long arms

dinosaurs.name: Gastonia
dinosaurs.description: About as long as a train car. Weighed as much as a Black Rhinoceros. Ate mainly low lying plants and leaves. Gastonia was hunted by Utahraptor. Ran at a speed of about 8 miles per hour. Was probably a herd animal

dinosaurs.name: Dilong
dinosaurs.description: Was as long as a human is tall. Weighed as much as a turkey. Run as fast as a road runner. Lived in what is now China. Name means “emperor dragon”. May have been warm blooded. May have had feathers

dinosaurs.name: Sinraptor
dinosaurs.description: Ran as fast as a Polar Bear. Was half the length of a school bus. Weighed as much as 2 Arabian horses. Lived in what is now Asia. Was as tall as a 1 story home

dinosaurs.name: Guanlong
dinosaurs.description: Guanlong was a car link long. Weighed as much as a large dog. Lived in what is now Asia. Was related to Tyrannosaurus Rex. Was a carnivore

dinosaurs.name: Pentaceratops
dinosaurs.description: Was 2 car links long. As tall as a 1 story house. Lived in North America. Weighed as much as an African Elephant. Could ram predators like a rhinoceros
